# GoalifyNow Mobile

## Scope

`mobile/` hosts the Tauri project; the web UI is built from `apps/webapp`.

## Practices

- Use the `package.json` scripts under `mobile/` for iOS and Android dev and release builds
- Preserve safe-area and touch-target guidance already used in the web app when adjusting shell or webview-related layout
- Keep API host resolution consistent with web environment configuration; avoid hardcoded machine IPs in source
- Validate critical flows on both iOS and Android when changing navigation or deep links
